 his clients but also for our community.</p>\n<h2>Thomas J Henry &#8211; Making Texas Safer :30 TV Commercial</h2>\n<div>\n<div id=\"schema-videoobject\" class=\"video-container\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/y0MaJD1GUDQ?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0\" width=\"853\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe></div>\n<p>Thomas J Henry, doing his part to make Texas safer while using his determination and resources to get his clients what they deserve.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","title":"Thomas J. Henry Making Texas Safer","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Thomas J. Henry Making Texas Safer","url":"/thomas-j-henry-making-texas-a-safer-place/"}],"title":"Thomas J. Henry - Making Texas Safer | The PM Group","metaDesc":"Thomas J. Henry debuted his new commercial which displays his commitment to his clients and community. Watch his new commercial \"Making Texas Safer\".","focuskw":"","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Thomas J. Henry - Making Texas Safer | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"Thomas J. Henry debuted his new commercial which displays his commitment to his clients and community. Watch his new commercial \"Making Texas Safer\".","opengraphImage":{"altText":"","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Thomas-J.-Henry-Making-Texas-Safer.png","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Thomas-J.-Henry-Making-Texas-Safer-300x157.png 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Thomas-J.-Henry-Making-Texas-Safer-1024x537.png 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Thomas-J.-Henry-Making-Texas-Safer-768x403.png 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Thomas-J